You probably don't.
你很可能不去。

10
00:00:22,540 --> 00:00:24,600
I know I don't go every six months.
我知道我自己就没做到每六个月去一次。

11
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:28,580
So yeah, we're going to be going to the dentist and of course we're going to be looking at
所以，是的，我们要去牙医那里，当然我们也会学习

