让我们先看第一个。

19
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:50,480
Toothache.
牙痛。

20
00:00:50,480 --> 00:00:51,480
Toothache.
牙痛。

21
00:00:51,480 --> 00:00:52,480
Toothache.
牙痛。

22
00:00:52,480 --> 00:00:53,480
Toothache.
牙痛。

23
00:00:53,480 --> 00:00:58,680
Okay, so we've seen before this ending ache, right?
好的，我们之前见过这个后缀“ache”，对吧？

24
00:00:58,680 --> 00:00:59,680
Right.
对。

25
