So again, a toothache would be?
那么，“toothache”就是？

28
00:01:02,680 --> 00:01:03,680
A hurting tooth.
牙齿疼。

29
00:01:03,680 --> 00:01:04,680
A hurting tooth.
牙齿疼。

30
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:05,680
Yes.
是的。

31
